metadata.name: Octogang #1
metadata.description:
Octogang is a family friendly community of creators and collectors journeying together with 2 simple brand missions.   
1. To create and innovate.
2. To raise awareness about ocean conservation through children education.

Owning an octo grants you membership to the gang and it's future perks.
All gangs are stupidly adorable, so you can choose to go for the rarer traits,
or look for octos that match your vibes. Remember, Be Silly, Have Fun, and Stay Truthful.

Are you ready to take the handshake?   
-Octogang üêôü§ùüêô
